{"tid":1680293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"ARU英國安格里亞魯斯金大學決定撤回何君堯名譽博士學位","createTime":"2019-10-28T17:23:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T01:29:05.000Z","uid":302471,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7b1931e282ecf08ce1367abb25bbabd96e1b6a14","tid":1680293,"uid":302471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T17:23:04.000Z","msg":"After request for comment from the Spectator, and after growing calls on social media for the university to investigate Ho&rsquo;s position, <span style=\"color: red;\">ARU have announced that they are withdrawing Ho&rsquo;s honorary degree</span>. In a statement, the university said:<br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;ARU&rsquo;s honorands must be positive role models to our students, alumni and staff, and to the communities we serve. Mr Ho&rsquo;s conduct since he was honoured has caused increasing concern. Following an investigation, the university has withdrawn Mr Ho&rsquo;s honorary degree.&rsquo;<br />\n<br />\n報道媒體The Spectator: Anglia Ruskin University strips Junius Ho of his honorary degree<br />\n<a href=\"https://blogs.spectator.co.uk/2019/10/anglia-ruskin-university-strips-junius-ho-of-his-honorary-degree/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblogs.spectator.co.uk%2F2019%2F10%2Fanglia-ruskin-university-strips-junius-ho-of-his-honorary-degree%2F&d=SKXI%2FGePWbtdtN3kaacFP6nyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=2f5e1984\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://blogs.spectator.co.uk/2019/10/anglia-ruskin-university-strips-junius-ho-of-his-honorary-degree/</a><br />\n<br />\n報道作者英國保守黨人權委員會委員Luke de Pulford<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/lukedepulford/status/1188860738842087426\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flukedepulford%2Fstatus%2F1188860738842087426&d=SKXI%2FGePWbtdtN3kaacFP6nyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=295bed60\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flukedepulford%2Fstatus%2F1188860738842087426&h=7e534bc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/lukedepulford/status/1188860738842087426</a><br />\n<br />\nARU未刪除何君堯資料<br />\n<a href=\"https://aru.ac.uk/graduation-and-alumni/honorary-award-holders2/junius-ho\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faru.ac.uk%2Fgraduation-and-alumni%2Fhonorary-award-holders2%2Fjunius-ho&d=SKXI%2FGePWbtdtN3kaacFP6nyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=58f136c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://aru.ac.uk/graduation-and-alumni/honorary-award-holders2/junius-ho</a>"},{"pid":"d2dc54c9687dc66935746a97e558b278fe81160a","tid":1680293,"uid":136893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T17:23:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記唔記得7、8月既時候，臨有行動前一日既連登，係充滿住遊行路線、離開方法、行動目的地既街坊整既攻略、仲有各種各樣既行動資訊整合，所有行動都係至小早半個月搞，有D 活動更加係會根據其重要性去調配，例如我記得葵青區遊行係推遲左成個月的。</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇下啦<br />\n<br />\n【正視聽：反思行動及行動數量】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1680287\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1680287</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8e59e9ed58709aea0cadb71a0eef213ced891ed9","tid":1680293,"uid":298093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T17:25:39.000Z","msg":"唔喺咁氹我開心下？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c4d91dfdb280b5807ce206cc68fad8392f6f2cd","tid":1680293,"uid":288107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T17:34:42.000Z","msg":"終於"},{"pid":"9e5ab2f233415034b6f1cd10f3ea20e297c7d924","tid":1680293,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T19:29:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UXnbdb6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUXnbd